Headers:
    packet_type
        1 --> producer to broker
                format: 'b 6s b'
                packet_type (1 byte), producer_ID (3 bytes) + stream_number (1 byte)
        2 --> producer broadcasts data to broker
                format: 'b 6s b i i'
                packet_type (1 byte), producer_ID (3 bytes) + stream_number (1 byte), frame (4 bytes), payload_size (4 bytes)


Making containers:
    docker create -ti --name broker --cap-add=all -v /Users/hazelhilbert/Documents/GitHub/NetworksA1:/compnets pythonimage /bin/bash
    docker network connect csnet broker
    docker start -i broker  
    python3 broker.py